headline: Bitcoin, Ethereum, Dogecoin, XRP Tumble After Trump Imposes Fresh Global Tariffs: Analyst Says BTC Approaching 'Final Leg Down' Of This Cycle
summary: Leading cryptocurrencies fell alongside stocks Sunday overnight after President Donald Trump said he’ll impose 15% global tariffs on U.S. imports.
